<p><span style="color: rgb(83, 83, 83); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 242); font-size: 24px;">会上，黄山松同志带领大家细细梳理了党章新修订的内容，对党章展开了全面学习，弘扬伟大建党精神，增强“四个意识”、坚定“四个自信”、做到“两个维护”，为全面建设社会主义现代化国家、全面推进中华民族伟大复兴而努力奋斗。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(83, 83, 83); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 250, 242); font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEIT8yIichn2d35xBHRWcnEzf2AobGV6cKgO7xicZE5oou2NMicu3nUB4mXSUHrF8TrrkiaUkMtG1S8pDA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="312" height="194" style="width: 312px; height: 194px;"/></span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 244, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; transform-style: preserve-3d;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; transform: translateZ(10px);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 20px;"><img data-ratio="1" data-type="gif" data-w="59" data-width="100%" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/2n18Qa8gmEIT8yIichn2d35xBHRWcnEzfgxcM8H9zh8VGtNNmbC7miacNDf2cuCMqsSe1cOtstHib9UPPrm2dX0Pw/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-original-style="box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: inherit;width: 100%;display: block;height: auto !important;" data-index="15" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/2n18Qa8gmEIT8yIichn2d35xBHRWcnEzfgxcM8H9zh8VGtNNmbC7miacNDf2cuCMqsSe1cOtstHib9UPPrm2dX0Pw/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" class="__bg_gif" _width="100%" __sec_open_place_holder__="true" data-order="2" alt="图片" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; vertical-align: inherit; width: 20px !important; display: block; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; transform: translateZ(5px);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(209, 68, 52); background-color: rgb(255, 243, 221); font-style: oblique; width: 30px; height: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(249, 240, 224); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(209, 68, 52); display: flex; align-items: center;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">钟宝乐</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section></section></section></section><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 10px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; border-left: 1px dashed rgb(209, 68, 52);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">通过此次例会学习，我回顾了四个意识，政治意识是根本、大局意识是关键、核心意识是保障、看齐意识是基础。增强四个意识，就是要保持清醒的政治头脑，在任何时候、任何情况下都要坚定理想信念，始终忠于党、忠于人民;就是要做到从大局出发,敢担当敢作为，履职尽责;就是要明确中国共产党是中国特色社会主义事业的领导核心，是实现中华民族伟大复兴的领导核心;就是要明确看齐是重大政治原则，是党的力量所在，优势所在。</span></p></section></section><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(248, 244, 236); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: flex-start;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; transform-style: preserve-3d;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; transform: translateZ(10px);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 20px;"><img data-ratio="1" data-type="gif" data-w="59" data-width="100%" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/2n18Qa8gmEIT8yIichn2d35xBHRWcnEzfgxcM8H9zh8VGtNNmbC7miacNDf2cuCMqsSe1cOtstHib9UPPrm2dX0Pw/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-original-style="box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: inherit;width: 100%;display: block;height: auto !important;" data-index="16" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/2n18Qa8gmEIT8yIichn2d35xBHRWcnEzfgxcM8H9zh8VGtNNmbC7miacNDf2cuCMqsSe1cOtstHib9UPPrm2dX0Pw/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" class="__bg_gif" _width="100%" __sec_open_place_holder__="true" data-order="3" alt="图片" data-fail="0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; vertical-align: inherit; width: 20px !important; display: block; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section><section style="margin: -10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; transform: translateZ(5px);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(209, 68, 52); background-color: rgb(255, 243, 221); font-style: oblique; width: 30px; height: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px 0px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(249, 240, 224); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(209, 68, 52); display: flex; align-items: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">舒李曦彤</strong></span></section></section></section></section><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 10px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; border-left: 1px dashed rgb(209, 68, 52);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我这次主要学习了新旧党章的对比，通过对新党章的学习，我了解到自觉遵守党的章程是作为一个党员最基本的要求，要保持党员的先进性就必须自觉遵守党的章程，遵守国家法律，在贯彻党的路线方针政策上坚定不移，不折不扣，更加深刻地认识到新党章的含义以及对党员的职责要求，时刻牢记自己是党的人，是党组织的一员，时刻不忘党员的义务和责任，把加强党性修养作为自己立身、立业、立言、立德的基石，坚定理想信念，加强对党的基本知识的了解。</span></p></section></section><p></p><p><br/></p>